# global options--------------------------------------------------------
Create Near # create folders locally
SyncState * # put syncstate files in respective folders
Expunge Both

# johninman ---------------------------------------------------------------

# Remote
IMAPStore johninman-remote
Host mail.privateemail.com
User john@johninman.dev
PassCmd "cat ~/.passwords/johninman"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

# Local
MaildirStore johninman-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/johninman/
Inbox ~/.mail/johninman/INBOX

Channel johninman
Far :johninman-remote:
Near :johninman-local:
Patterns INBOX Drafts Sent "Archive/*" Trash

